Components of IAM:------------------------------------------------

Users:

Groups --> Many users together form a group. Collection of IAM users.
You can use IAM groups to specify permissions for multiple users.
Any permission applied to the group are applied to the users inside 
this group.
A new person joins the company. You can add him to the proper group and 
he will have that group permissions automatically.

Policies --> Engines that allows or deny a connection. Based on policies
one gets access or NO access to resources.

Roles --> Temporary credentials 



https://www.simplilearn.com/tutorials/aws-tutorial/aws-iam
